Question:
====================Question====================
                    
Study the each pair of expressions given in Expressions column and match them with appropriate operator present in Relations column
                    
\[
        \begin{array}{|c|c|c|c|}
        \hline
        \text{ } & \text{Operations} & \text{ } & \text{Relations} \\ 
        \hline
        a & 0+5,0-6 & 1 & =  \\
        \hline
        b & 0+8,2*5 & 2 & < \\
        \hline
        c & 8-9,4-5 & 3 & >  \\ 
        \hline
        \end{array}
        \]
Solution_text:
Evaluate each pair of equation and compare it by doing so you will get solution for each pair as follows-
In expressions - $8-9,4-5$
$LHS = 8-9 = -1$
$RHS = 4-5 = -1$
$LHS = RHS$
In expressions - $0+8,2*5$
$LHS = 0+8 = 8$
$RHS = 2*5 = 10$
$LHS < RHS$
In expressions - $0+5,0-6$
$LHS = 0+5 = 5$
$RHS = 0-6 = -6$
$LHS > RHS$

Thus the correct option is - a-3 b-2 c-1
